Color Bars
A program to display color bars
SCREEN, FOR/NEXT/STEP, LINE, RGB
10 SCREEN 2
20 FOR X=1 TO 255 STEP 2
30 LINE X+20,30,X+20,50,RGB(X,0,0)
40 LINE X+20,80,X+20,100,RGB(0,X,0)
50 LINE X+20,130,X+20,150,RGB(0,0,X)
60 LINE X+20,180,X+20,200,RGB(X,X,0)
70 LINE X+20,230,X+20,250,RGB(0,X,X)
80 LINE X+20,280,X+20,300,RGB(X,0,X)
90 NEXT
